{"tid":2076070,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：林鄭月娥全家可能在兩周內被取消英國國籍","createTime":"2020-06-23T09:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T15:58:22.000Z","uid":74295,"like":341,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":73,"remark":"[gold]⚠️ 管理團隊警示：本主題內容已被回報為「真實性有待確定，及可能含有虛假資訊」，請各位留意。[/gold]\n警示措拖說明：https://lih.kg/eobQbT","replies":[{"pid":"7a2302653e1181476ebf764820c7222d6ea371a1","tid":2076070,"uid":74295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:11:47.000Z","msg":"英國內政部：將撤銷林鄭月娥全家英國國籍 消息人士引英國內政部不願透露其他姓名官員，預計英國政府將在兩周內正式宣佈取消鄭月娥全家英國國籍。 該官員強調，英國幾個世紀以來都在堅守英國價值與通行的文明規則。英國不會因爲雙向對等商業利益而放棄自己文明底綫。<br />\n<br />\n香港人民的反抗運動已經持續了12個月，英國採取一些實際行動，包括取消推動《逃犯條例》修訂草案的港府官員及其家人的英國國籍。該報道綜合媒體消息，一位名為「Deeran Kumar」<a href=\"http://的香港網友四周前在Change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E5%9B%9B%E5%91%A8%E5%89%8D%E5%9C%A8Change.org&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=9b7ff2f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">的香港網友四周前在Change.org</a>上發起連署，他於連署書上表示，「在香港政府引用《緊急法》通過《禁蒙面法》，而法律卻不及於香港警察，可見政府機關在法律之前並不平等，這顯示香港已非法治社會，並進入緊急狀態，因此，英國內政部撤銷林鄭月娥一家的英國公民身分」；對此，Deeran Kumar還特別指出林鄭的丈夫及兩個兒子的名字，並稱其兩個兒子皆於英國定居、讀書。<br />\n<br />\n該報道說，在連署書的最後，「Deeran Kumar」強調，「我誠摯相信，英國對遏制香港的暴力行為須負道德責任，有鑒於林鄭月娥拒負香港特首責任並施行嚴刑峻法，英國內政部應該永久撤銷林鄭月娥一家的公民身分」。<br />\n<br />\n據該報道引述消息說，林鄭月娥與丈夫林兆波於英國劍橋結識，1984年結婚，育有兩子，父子三人均持有英國國籍，而林鄭月娥則於2007年因擔任發展局局長放棄英國國籍。<br />\n強調，「我誠摯相信，英國對遏制香港的暴力行為須負道德責任，有鑑於林鄭月娥拒負香港特首責任並施行嚴刑峻法，英國內政部永久撤銷林鄭月娥一家的公民身分」<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"http://chiyidavip.com/doc_a1Q1U2hPZko2T1Z2YkVQNU1PZVluUT09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchiyidavip.com%2Fdoc_a1Q1U2hPZko2T1Z2YkVQNU1PZVluUT09&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=e74d7c14\" target=\"_blank\">http://chiyidavip.com/doc_a1Q1U2hPZko2T1Z2YkVQNU1PZVluUT09</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ccc3bca749852f4b0978bcdd37a13e4b2359a21","tid":2076070,"uid":125168,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:12:31.000Z","msg":"唔好哄我開心"},{"pid":"b6acfddf351b66253bd0ea3686ac0c0f013c0885","tid":2076070,"uid":208118,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:12:37.000Z","msg":"content farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1518cdf8e8585c503a9c3712778d03c2ab5f4b","tid":2076070,"uid":125168,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"b6acfddf351b66253bd0ea3686ac0c0f013c0885","tid":2076070,"uid":208118,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:12:37.000Z","msg":"content farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:13:18.000Z","msg":"個網仲假過content farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1095c1976d5bddfcd8cef7d61117e5f94148d0d","tid":2076070,"uid":167928,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:13:27.000Z","msg":"農場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515b34b5afbc2f163fb625728cc037a909fa7163","tid":2076070,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bc42d8a57327d1c2d6bdcb9061ebeeccf91ec7","tid":2076070,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:14:38.000Z","msg":"好假"},{"pid":"5a6682fe194317f310f2048856dfc5f5daf3d8cd","tid":2076070,"uid":74295,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:14:48.000Z","msg":"希望呢個content farm有啲堅料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae94e7b8470fb85ebbe983be5e2601e0536b455","tid":2076070,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:15:08.000Z","ms